{"tid":1457543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實散水撚係唔撚係全連登最廢?最無貢獻?","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:32.000Z","uid":31637,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb92f6fe3d22c1a8448e2be58867572d551c2a7","tid":1457543,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"1. 部份和理非抗爭=好似甘地咁捱打,之後博更多人同情<br />\n2.勇武革命=用自己條命同人地同歸於盡, 一命換一命,或一命換變命<br />\n<br />\n連登既散水撚完撚全冇條件搞和理非抗爭或勇武革命<br />\n最撚盡只可以搞三罷, 相信連搞罷交稅都怕死"},{"pid":"26c339eee90de3f8cb313b480877b633e7325016","tid":1457543,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJYVJsN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJYVJsN.jpg&h=15362e78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5e32a0c4281724ebac88310e387e8b5997e89a3","tid":1457543,"uid":178791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想走想留, 自己諗"},{"pid":"0de766c690b3f50087376f3aa333e512645fc061","tid":1457543,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 部份和理非抗爭=好似甘地咁捱打,之後博更多人同情<br />\n2.勇武革命=用自己條命同人地同歸於盡, 一命換一命,或一命換<span style=\"color: red;\">幾</span>命<br />\n<br />\n連登既散水撚完撚全冇條件搞和理非抗爭或勇武革命<br />\n最撚盡只可以搞三罷, 相信連搞罷交稅都怕死</blockquote>"},{"pid":"eaf92539294b6f1cd37bd9cb14c669d3d69d76f3","tid":1457543,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1EqkSM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1EqkSM.png&h=a2cdd3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四點突然成班P牌開post<br />\n然後一堆假消息、改圖出現<br />\n然後六點鐘  所有P牌消失<br />\n發生乜事大家心知肚明"},{"pid":"20434e3ca7ca53e314eb992b37a4749e26cfdbb9","tid":1457543,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf92539294b6f1cd37bd9cb14c669d3d69d76f3","tid":1457543,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1EqkSM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1EqkSM.png&h=a2cdd3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四點突然成班P牌開post<br />\n然後一堆假消息、改圖出現<br />\n然後六點鐘  所有P牌消失<br />\n發生乜事大家心知肚明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:53:50.000Z","msg":"p牌消失係連仔做野<br />\n禁p點讚點開post"},{"pid":"7bed75387cf257f85e9b97b4c013e8f28f4ec64d","tid":1457543,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:32.000Z","msg":"建議散水撚唔想人送頭可以做一樣野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係做情報兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不斷收集大量資訊並FC左再交出黎<br />\nD訊息越新鮮、越多、越正確<br />\n咁現場人士自然會推斷到要唔要走同幾點走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有人包括和理非同前線手足都無人想送頭，而唯一幫助到佢地安全咁行動既就只有情報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n仲有就係唔理咩人都好，唔好再大量開「留守」或「散水」既post，你地要互罵唔該係返個post入面鬧飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場好多時係只可以斷斷續續咁上到網，好多時load好耐先睇到少少野，如果真正有用既資訊就咁比你地d垃圾post洗走晒，咁出左事果陣就係你地呢堆不停開post互罵既人有份害佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果情況持續，經常發夢既人最好block左呢d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"}]}